channel.title: Browsers Shitting on me
channel.description: ^ Pretty much the title. I can only open Internet Explorer and, it's not the browser I'd prefer. I've tried to open Firefox, Chrome, and Opera and none of them work. When I go into the task manager I see that their processes are running, but the browsers just don't work. I've had this problem for like a month and I'm getting tired of it. Any solutions?

item.title: Browsers Shitting on me
item.dc:creator: Maverix26
item.description:
I LITERALLY, just had this probleem about an hour ago. Apparently, my modem was on it’s rag or something. Turn it off for like 10 seconds, then turn it back on.

If your situation is similiar to mine, other programs that use internet, like skype, or steam, work perfectly, where as browsers don’t work at all.
